{{!< default}}
<main class="sprint16-home" id="main">
  <section class="s16-hero" id="start-here" aria-labelledby="s16-title">
    <div class="shell s16-hero-grid">
      <div class="s16-hero-copy">
        <p class="s16-promise">Respect your time.<br><strong>Earn your trust.</strong><br>Improve your decisions.</p>
        <p class="s16-eyebrow">THE BUSINESS OF MEDICINE</p>
        <h1 id="s16-title">Make the next physician decision clearer.</h1>
        <p class="s16-lead">Practical decision intelligence for the questions that shape your career, practice, and financial future.</p>
        <a class="s16-button" href="#featured-decision">Start with today’s decision <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
      </div>

      <aside class="s16-progress-panel" aria-labelledby="progress-title">
        <div class="s16-panel-top"><p class="s16-eyebrow">YOUR PROGRESS</p><span>PRIVATE</span></div>
        <h2 id="progress-title">Your decision score</h2>
        <strong class="s16-score">0<span>/100</span></strong>
        <p>Start one decision to build a private record of what you have explored.</p>
        <div class="s16-progress-track" aria-hidden="true"><span></span></div>
        <div class="s16-progress-meta"><span>0 decisions started</span><span>0 min invested</span></div>
      </aside>

      <aside class="s16-intelligence" id="how-it-works" aria-labelledby="intelligence-title">
        <p class="s16-eyebrow">PHYSICIAN DECISION INTELLIGENCE™</p>
        <h2 id="intelligence-title">Built around the choices physicians actually face.</h2>
        <p>Clear, useful context—at the depth your time allows.</p>
        <a href="{{@site.url}}/methodology/">How it works <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="s16-featured" id="featured-decision" aria-labelledby="featured-title">
    <div class="shell">
      <div class="s16-section-heading"><p class="s16-eyebrow">FEATURED DECISION</p><p>Choose the depth that fits the moment.</p></div>
      <div class="s16-featured-grid">
        <article class="s16-decision-intro">
          <p class="s16-topic">COMPENSATION</p>
          <h2 id="featured-title">Are you getting paid what you’re worth?</h2>
          <p>See the compensation formula most physicians never receive—and the questions to ask before your next conversation.</p>
        </article>
        <div class="s16-depths" id="questions" aria-label="Decision learning depths">
          <a href="{{@site.url}}/briefs/" class="s16-depth-card"><span>BIG PICTURE</span><strong>30 sec</strong><p>See what matters.</p><b>Start here →</b></a>
          <a href="{{@site.url}}/briefs/" class="s16-depth-card s16-depth-card--primary"><span>BRIEF OVERVIEW</span><strong>2 min</strong><p>Understand the formula.</p><b>Explore →</b></a>
          <a href="{{@site.url}}/briefs/" class="s16-depth-card"><span>DEEP DIVE</span><strong>5 min</strong><p>Prepare for the conversation.</p><b>Go deeper →</b></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="s16-next" id="next-decisions" aria-labelledby="next-title">
    <div class="shell">
      <div class="s16-section-heading"><div><p class="s16-eyebrow">NEXT UP</p><h2 id="next-title">What physicians are deciding next</h2></div><div class="s16-carousel-controls" aria-label="Carousel controls"><button type="button" aria-label="Previous decisions">←</button><button type="button" aria-label="Next decisions">→</button></div></div>
      <div class="s16-carousel" aria-label="Upcoming physician decisions">
        <article><p>EMPLOYMENT</p><h3>Would you sign your contract again today?</h3><span>Big Picture · 30 sec</span></article>
        <article><p>ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE</p><h3>Could AI give you one clinic back every week?</h3><span>Brief Overview · 2 min</span></article>
        <article><p>PRACTICE OWNERSHIP</p><h3>Should you own your practice—or stay employed?</h3><span>Deep Dive · 5 min</span></article>
        <article><p>PERSONAL FINANCE</p><h3>Are you building wealth—or only earning income?</h3><span>Big Picture · 30 sec</span></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
